%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%2C%2020%2C%20Found%20Dead%20In%20Bengaluru%20Home%20With%20Slit%20Marks%20On%20Neck%2C%20Wrist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2020-year-old%20woman%20was%20found%20dead%20inside%20the%20bathroom%20of%20her%20home%20in%20Bengaluru%20yesterday.%20She%20was%20found%20dead%20with%20slit%20marks%20on%20her%20neck%20and%20wrist%20of%20her%20left%20hand%2C%20said%20police.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%20evening%2C%20the%20woman's%20brother%20kept%20knocking%20on%20the%20bathroom%20door%20but%20there%20was%20no%20response.%20The%20door%20was%20then%20struck%20down%20only%20to%20find%20the%20woman%20lying%20dead%20on%20the%20bathroom%20floor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20says%20a%20suicide%20note%20has%20been%20discovered%2C%20however%2C%20the%20woman's%20mother%20denies%20that%20she%20killed%20herself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20around%207.30%20pm%20yesterday%2C%20a%2020-year-old%20woman%20was%20found%20dead%20under%20suspicious%20circumstances.%20Prima%20facie%2C%20according%20to%20the%20information%20available%2C%20her%20hand%20and%20neck%20were%20cut%2C%20and%20she%20died%20of%20blood%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20police.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDCP%20South%20S.%20Lokesh%20Jagalsar%20said%20that%20they%20are%20investigating%20the%20case%20from%20all%20angles%20and%20are%20waiting%20for%20the%20post-mortem%20report%20to%20determine%20whether%20this%20was%20a%20suicide%20or%20murder.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20expecting%20the%20post%20mortem%20report.%20We%20will%20investigate%20the%20case%20from%20all%20angles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20mother%2C%20who%20is%20a%20social%20activist%2C%20said%20that%20she%20wants%20justice%20for%20her%20daughter.%20Devastated%20by%20the%20loss%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20raised%20her%20with%20so%20much%20love.%20No%20matter%20what%2C%20she%20would%20face%20everything%20with%20courage.%20She%20always%20used%20to%20tell%20me%20everything.%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20happened%20this%20time.%20I%20am%20an%20activist.%20I%20have%20rescued%20and%20questioned%20so%20many%20people.%20If%20someone%20had%20a%20grudge%2C%20they%20may%20have%20caused%20this.%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20happened%20to%20her.%20I%20want%20justice.%20She%20was%20a%20courageous%20girl.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715860920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F2fcolnuo_prabhudya_625x300_16_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fwoman-20-found-dead-in-bengaluru-home-with-slit-marks-on-neck-wrist-5677282%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2020-year-old%20woman%20was%20found%20dead%20inside%20the%20bathroom%20of%20her%20home%20in%20Bengaluru%20yesterday.%20She%20was%20found%20dead%20with%20slit%20marks%20on%20her%20neck%20and%20wrist%20of%20her%20left%20hand%2C%20said%20police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fwoman-20-found-dead-in-bengaluru-home-with-slit-marks-on-neck-wrist-5677282%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fwoman-20-found-dead-in-bengaluru-home-with-slit-marks-on-neck-wrist-5677282%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fwoman-20-found-dead-in-bengaluru-home-with-slit-marks-on-neck-wrist-5677282%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It's%20Raining%20In%20Hyderabad%20Ahead%20Of%20SRH-GT%20Game.%20How%20It'll%20Impact%20Playoffs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20will%20see%20an%20important%20clash%20between%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad%20and%20Gujarat%20Titans%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20IPL%202024%20playoff%20race%20will%20be%20hugely%20impacted%20by%20the%20result%20of%20this%20match.%20So%20far%2C%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(19%20points%20in%2013%20matches)%20