nister%2C%20the%20court%20said%20it%20would%20not%20go%20into%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judges%20also%20put%20aside%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20argument%20%E2%80%93%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20comment%20that%20if%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20wins%2C%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bnot%20have%20to%20go%20back%20to%20jail%26quot%3B%20--%20is%20a%20contempt%20of%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bassumption%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20the%20judges%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20order%20is%20very%20clear%20about%20when%20he%20has%20to%20surrender.%20It%20is%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20rule%20of%20law%20shall%20be%20governed%20by%20this%20order%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715860020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F1j4dmcak_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_11_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-exception-in-bail-to-arvind-kejriwal-supreme-court-amid-criticism-5676946%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20release%20on%20interim%20bail%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20an%20exception%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%20after%20the%20government%20complained%20that%20its%20decision%20has%20been%20criticised%20by%20many.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-exception-in-bail-to-arvind-kejriwal-supreme-court-amid-criticism-5676946%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-exception-in-bail-to-arvind-kejriwal-supreme-court-amid-criticism-5676946%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-exception-in-bail-to-arvind-kejriwal-supreme-court-amid-criticism-5676946%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suspect%20charged%20with%20attempted%20murder%20of%20Slovak%20PM%20Fico%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22