y%20treasures.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20his%20parents%2C%20Subrat%20believes%20in%20giving%20traditional%20fertilisers%20to%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20fruiting%20plant%20requires%20nitrogen%20for%20leaves%20and%20stem%20growth%2C%20phosphorus%20for%20root%20development%2C%20and%20potash%20for%20flower%20and%20fruit%20growth.%20We%20get%20these%20nutrients%20in%20cow%20dung%20itself.%20I%20do%20not%20make%20any%20other%20fancy%20fertilisers.%20Cow%20dung%20is%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Subrat%20does%20not%20aim%20to%20sell%20the%20Miyazaki%20mangoes%2C%20he%20does%20sell%20saplings%20of%20the%20rare%201%2C000%20petal%20lotus%20and%20other%20water%20lily%20varieties.%20Last%20year%2C%20he%20earned%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20through%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20grow%20any%20rare%20plant%2C%20one%20must%20do%20a%20detailed%20study%20on%20the%20kind%20of%20temperature%20and%20humidity%20they%20require%20and%20the%20pot%20size.%20For%20instance%2C%20I%20grow%20the%201%2C000%20petal%20lotus%20in%20a%20bigger%20pot%20of%204%20ft%20width%20and%202%20ft%20of%20depth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhereas%2C%20I%20use%20a%20pot%20of%20one%20ft%20width%20and%20seven%20inch%20depth%20for%20micro%20lotuses.%20We%20must%20also%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20lotuses%20and%20water%20lilies%20do%20not%20thrive%20in%20hard%20water%20and%20require%206%20to%207%20hours%20of%20sunlight%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubrat%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20a%20pro.%20Growing%20rare%20plants%20is%20just%20my%20hobby%20and%20these%20plants%20are%20my%20only%20treasures.%20Also%2C%20I%20come%20across%20many%20people%20who%20make%20excuses%20that%20they%20cannot%20grow%20plants%20because%20of%20small%20spaces.%20With%20my%20example%2C%20I%20want%20to%20show%20that%20anyone%20can%20grow%20plants%2C%20even%20the%20rarest%20ones%20at