r-agreed-to-reveal-where-he-buried-her-54-years-ago-13136972%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpolice-to-dig-again-for-muriel-mckay-after-killer-agreed-to-reveal-where-he-buried-her-54-years-ago-13136972%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpolice-to-dig-again-for-muriel-mckay-after-killer-agreed-to-reveal-where-he-buried-her-54-years-ago-13136972%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ponting%2C%20IPL%20Coach%2C%20Ex-IND%20Pacer%3A%20Report%20Reveals%20Choices%20For%20IND%20Coach%20Job%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20head%20coach%20for%20the%20men's%20cricket%20team%20as%20Rahul%20Dravid's%20stint%20will%20come%20to%20an%20end%20after%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%2C%20and%20if%20he%20wishes%20to%20continue%2C%20he%20would%20have%20to%20re-apply%20for%20the%20position%2C%20which%20the%20veteran%20has%20been%20reportedly%20denying%20so%20far.%20The%20multi-format%20coaching%20role%20requires%20the%20coach%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20team%20for%20approximately%20ten%20months%20with%20the%20busy%20men's%20team%20calendar.%20IANS%20understands%20that%20Dravid%20is%20ready%20to%20step%20down%20from%20the%20position%20regardless%20of%20the%20fact%20whether%20it%20ends%20with%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20title%20or%20not%20and%20wishes%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20South%20Africa%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20England%20divide%20their%20coaching%20responsibilities%20between%20red-ball%20and%20white-ball%20cricket%2C%20the%20BCCI%20is%20still%20unwilling%20to%20adopt%20a%20similar%20strategy%20because%20India%20do%20not%20have%20two%20distinct%20player%20groups%20for%20two%20formats.%20The%20BCCI%20also%20approached%20ex-Indian%20players%20for%20the%20position%20but%20they%20will%20have%20to%20fill%20the%20application%20form%20to%20stay%20alive%20in%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20speculation%20said%20that%20VVS%20Laxman%20would%20succeed%20Dravid%20in%20the%20role%20which%20he%20previously%20filled%20on%20a%20part-time%20basis%20in%20the%20latter's%20absence%20last%20year.%20However%2C%20sources%20confirmed%20that%20Laxman%20is%20not%20in%20the%20mood%20to%20apply%20and%20will%20continue%20with%20the%20India%20%E2%80%98A'%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Australian%20cricketer%20and%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%20head%20coach%20Justin%20Langer%20is%20also%20in%20the%20fray%20for%20the%20head%20coach%20position%20along%20with%20other%20star%20veterans%20including%20Stephen%20Fleming%2C%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20Ashish%20Nehra.%20BCCI%20has%20also%20been%20meeting%20with%20IPL%20coaches%20and%20mentors%20in%20the%20hunt%20for%20a%20head%20coach.%20Langer%20%E2%80%98is%20curious'%20and%20interested%20in%20coaching%20the%20Indian%20team%20but%20according%20to%20sources%2C%20Ponting%20had%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20BCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20and%20chief%20selector%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20in%20Delhi%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20the%20month%20regarding%20the%20coaching%20position.%20Ponting%20is%20currently%20associated%20with%20IPL%20franchise%20Delhi%20Capitals%20as%20head%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCCI%20can%20also%20look%20up%20to%20Gambhir%2C%20who%20returned%20back%20to%20his%20old%20franchise%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20after%20serving%20two%20years%20at%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%20and%20has%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20steering%20the%20side%20to%20back-to-back%20playoff%20finishes.%20Gujarat%20Titans%20head%20coach%20Nehra%20has%20also%20shown%20interest%20in%20guiding%20the%20Indian%20team%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20not%2C%20if%20I%20would%20be%20given%20a%20chance%20to%20coach%20the%20Indian%20team%20why%20won't%20I.%20I%20believe%20the%20team%20not%20only%20revolves%20around%20the%20captain%20it's%20the%20management%20that%20plays%20the%20key%20role%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nehra%20had%20said%20in%20an%20event%20back%20in%202021.%20Also%2C%20Nehra%20has%20proved%20his%20managing%20mettle%20with%20GT%2C%20winning%20the%20IPL%20in%20their%20debut%20season%20and%20a%20runner-up%20finish%20in%20the%20next%20edition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Dravid%20is%20%E2%80%98not%20interested'%20in%20extending%20his%20role%20and%20Laxman%20wants%20to%20stick%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98A'%20team%20it%20is%20Ponting%20who%20is%20the%20front-runner%20in%20the%20race%20but%20the%20extensive%20ten%20months%20working%20load%20in%20away%20conditions%20will%20be%20the%20key%20point%20in%20his%20decision.%20Also%2C%20Ponting%20was%20appointed%20head%20coach%20of%20Washington%20Freedom%20ahead%20of%20the%20second%20season%20of%20Major%20League%20Cricket%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20start%20form%20July%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20end%20of%20T20%20WC%2C%20India%20will%20be%20travelling%20to%20Zimbabwe%20for%20a%20five-match%20T20I%20series%20starting%20from%20July%2015.%20So%2C%20with%20MLC%20ending%20on%20June%2029%2C%20and%20Ponting%20serving%20Washington%20Freedom%20in%20the%20USA%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20very%20difficult%20job%20for%20the%20BCCI%20and%20the%20former%20Australian%20skipper%20to%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCCI%20can%20also%20look%20for%20other%20options%20such%20as%20Stephen%20Fleming%2C%20who%20is%20the%20longest-serving%20coach%20in%20IPL%20for%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings.%20Dravid%2C%20who%20was%20given%20a%20six-month%20extension%20post%20the%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20in%20October-November%2C%20has%20his%20contract%20expiring%20after%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20next%20month.%20The%20former%20India%20captain%20has%20the%20option%20of%20re-applying%20for%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20board%20on%20Monday%20invited%20applications%20for%20the%20role%20with%20a%20deadline%20of%20May%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%