-epsteins-1997-little-black-book-now-for-sale%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20of%20221%20individuals%20who%20are%20not%20included%20in%20the%20more%20well-known%20later%20version%20that%20was%20initially%20released%20by%20Gawker%20in%202015%20are%20contained%20in%20the%20personal%20address%20book.%20Bill%20Panagopulos%2C%20owner%20of%20Alexander%20Historical%20Auctions%2C%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20book.%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20I%20know%2C%20Mr.%20Epstein's%20estate%20is%20in%20no%20way%20involved%20in%20any%20manner.%20As%20for%20the%20proceeds%20of%20the%20sale%2C%20I%20can%20say%20with%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20confidence%20that%20they%20will%20be%20going%20to%20a%20party%20that%20does%20not%2C%20nor%20ever%20did%20have%20any%20connection%20with%20Mr.%20Epstein%20or%20anyone%20named%20in%20the%20book%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20forensic%20document%20examiner%20dated%20the%2064-page%20address%20book%20from%201997%20and%20said%20that%20it%20contains%20a%20total%20of%20349%20names.%20Similar%20to%20Epstein's%20other%20book%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20people%20who%20are%20included%20have%20denied%20ever%20meeting%20or%20being%20associated%20with%20the%20financier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alexautographs.com%2Fjeffrey-epsteins-little-black-book%2F%5C%22%3Ecompany%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20item%20description%20states%20that%20the%20book%20is%20bound%20in%20black%20plastic%20and%20has%20dimensions%20of%204.5%20x%205.25%20inches.%20The%20entries%20are%20printed%20copies%20that%20have%20%26quot%3Blikely%20reduced%20in%20size%20to%20accommodate%20this%20rather%20small%20binding.%26quot%3B%20The%20bidding%20began%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20will%20go%20on%20for%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20auction%20house%20stated%20that%20the%20names%20have%20%26quot%3Bblack%2C%20hand-applied%20checkmarks%2C%20and%20five%20have%20been%20highlighted%20in%20yellow%26quot%3B.%20The%20names%20are%20%26quot%3Bwell-recognized%20financial%20and%20industrial%20figures%26quot%3B%20including%20Mr%20Trump.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20unknown%20what%20the%20checked%20and%20highlighted%20names%20mean.%20Further%2C%20it%20also%20has%20%26quot%3Ba%20good%20deal%20of%20information%20hinting%20at%20Epstein's%20sordid%20past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20auction%20company%20claims%20that%20a%20Manhattan-based%20musician%20found%20the%20book%20for%20sale%20when%20it%20was%20lying%20on%20a%20Fifth%20Avenue%20sidewalk%20in%20the%20mid-1990s.%20The%20book%20was%20kept%20by%20the%20woman%2C%20who%20didn't%20realise%20it%20belonged%20to%20Epstein%20until%202020%20when%20she%20was%20organising%20her%20storage%20unit.%20She%20contacted%20several%20media%20outlets%2C%20but%20none%20of%20them%20responded.%20Later%2C%20a%20PhD%20student%20eventually%20bought%20the%20book%20off%20of%20an%20eBay%20listing%20and%20had%20it%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20auctioneer%20stated%20that%20each%20bidder's%20identity%20will%20be%20kept%20confidential.%20If%20the%20seller%20declines%20the%20highest%20price%20tendered%2C%20the%20book%20will%20be%20put%20up%20for%20public%20auction%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715852400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2F3bo7qov_jeffrey-epstein-reuters_625x300_19_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeffrey-epsteins-original-little-black-book-could-fetch-200-000-at-auction-5676217%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20auction%20house%20stated%20that%20the%20names%20have%20%26quot%3Bblack%2C%20hand-applied%20checkmarks%2C%20and%20five%20have%20been%20highlighted%20in%20yellow%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeffrey-epsteins-original-little-black-book-could-fetch-200-000-at