hoarding-collapse-toll-rises-to-16-5673858%5C%22%3ECouple%20Found%20Dead%20In%20Car%20Under%20Mumbai%20Hoarding.%20They%20Had%20Stopped%20For%20Petrol%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20has%20now%20shifted%20to%20scrutinising%20the%20permits%20granted%20to%20such%20establishments%2C%20with%20the%20Mumbai%20metropolitan%20area%20mandating%20licenses%20overseen%20by%20the%20BMC%20for%20any%20business%20operations.%20Also%20under%20investigation%20are%20the%20provisional%20licenses%20issued%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20petrol%20pumps%2C%20particularly%20those%20replacing%20GRP%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20on%20which%20the%20petrol%20pump%20operates%20falls%20within%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20housing%20department%2C%20requiring%20approval%20from%20the%20Revenue%20Department%20for%20commercial%20use.%20Lack%20of%20clarity%20regarding%20how%20commercial%20activities%20were%20sanctioned%20at%20the%20site%20without%20obtaining%20permissions%20from%20the%20Revenue%20Department%20has%20prompted%20inquiries%20directed%20at%20the%20Police%20Housing%20Development%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20objections%20were%20raised%20by%20the%20Police%20Housing%20Development%20Corporation%20concerning%20construction%20activity%20at%20the%20petrol%20pump%20site.%20The%20corporation%2C%20responsible%20for%20housing%20solutions%20for%20police%20personnel%2C%20contends%20that%20the%20land%20was%20earmarked%20for%20government%20infrastructure%20or%20residential%20purposes%20for%20government%20employees.%20Despite%20objections%20and%20recommendations%20against%20the%20construction%20of%20petrol%20pumps%20on%20such%20lands%2C%20work%20commenced%20without%20securing%20governmental%20approvals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railway%20Commissioner%20sought%20permission%20from%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20(DGP)%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20project%2C%20citing%20potential%20revenue%20generation%20for%20police%20welfare%20initiatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20Bhavesh%20Bhinde%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20Ego%20Media%20Private%20Limited%2C%20the%20company%20responsible%20for%20erecting%20the%20hoarding%2C%20and%20additional%20suspects.%20The%20charges%20include%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%2C%20filed%20at%20Pant%20Nagar%20police%20station.%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Bhinde%20remains%20missing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20escalating%20concerns%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20Home%20Minister%20has%20issued%20directives%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20investigation%20into%20the%20case%2C%20assigning%20the%20responsibility%20to%20a%20DGP-ranked%20officer.%20Additionally%2C%20seven%20teams%20have%20been%20mobilised%20to%20track%20down%20the%20fugitive%20accused%2C%20with%20the%20latest%20lead%20tracing%20Bhinde's%20whereabouts%20to%20Lonavala.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715851980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F3mdb7tgg_ghatkopar-petrol-pump-pti_625x300_16_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-hoarding-collapse-petrol-pump-on-which-mumbai-billboard-fell-didnt-have-clearance-5676054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20petrol%20pump%2C%20on%20which%20a%20massive%20billboard%20came%20crashing%20down%20on%20Monday%2C%20killing%2016%20and%20injuring%20over%2040%20others%20in%20Mumbai's%20Ghatkopar%2C%20did%20not%20have%20an%20Occupancy%20Certificate%20(OC)%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-hoarding-collapse-petrol-pump-on-which-mumbai-billboard-fell-didnt-have-clearance-5676054%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-hoarding-collapse-petrol-pump-on-which-mumbai-billboard-fell-didnt-have-clearance-5676054%2Famp%2F1%22%