r%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20pointed%20out%20senior%20union%20ministers%20-%20whom%20he%20did%20not%20name%20-%20had%20made%20various%20kinds%20of%20statements%20against%20his%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-india-bloc-wins-on-june-4-ill-be-back-next-day-arvind-kejriwal-5656158%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIf%20INDIA%20Bloc%20Wins%20On%20June%204%2C%20I'll%20Be%20Back%20Next%20Day%3A%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20while%20campaigning%20for%20his%20party%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20he%20feared%20being%20thrown%20in%20jail%20again%20should%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20win%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20He%20also%20claimed%20efforts%20were%20made%2C%20after%20being%20sent%20to%20Delhi's%20Tihar%20Jail%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Bbreak%20and%20humiliate%26quot%3B%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20go%20back%20to%20jail%20on%20June%202.%20I%20will%20be%20watching%20the%20results%20(of%20the%20election)%20on%20June%204%20from%20jail.%20If%20you%20make%20INDIA%20bloc%20(the%20Congress-led%20opposition%20grouping%20of%20which%20the%20AAP%20is%20a%20member)%20win%2C%20I%20will%20come%20back%20on%20June%205.%20If%20there%20is%20lack%20of%20effort%2C%20let%20us%20see%20when%20we%20will%20meet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20last%20week%20also%20snubbed%20a%20petition%20seeking%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20removal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-bail-supreme-court-no-legal-merit-supreme-court-junks-another-plea-to-sack-arvind-kejriwal-5651938%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNo%20Legal%20Merit%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Junks%20Another%20Plea%20To%20Sack%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp