ws%2Fworld-europe-69019121.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MIT%20Graduates%20Arrested%20For%20Stealing%20%2425%20Million%20In%20Crypto%20In%2012%20Seconds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFederal%20prosecutors%20in%20Manhattan%20are%20accusing%20two%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT)%20graduates%20of%20pulling%20off%20a%20groundbreaking%20crypto%20heist.%20Anton%20and%20James%20Peraire-Bueno%2C%20aged%2024%20and%2028%20respectively%2C%20allegedly%20manipulated%20the%20Ethereum%20blockchain%20in%20a%20mere%2012%20seconds%2C%20stealing%20a%20staggering%20%2425%20million%20from%20unsuspecting%20traders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audacious%20scheme%2C%20dubbed%20%26quot%3Bnovel%26quot%3B%20by%20authorities%2C%20marks%20the%20first%20US%20criminal%20case%20involving%20such%20a%20blockchain%20exploit%2C%20reported%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F05%2F15%2Fbusiness%2Fmit-educated-brothers-allegedly-stole-25m-in-crypto-in-just-12-seconds%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20allege%2C%20the%20defendants'%20scheme%20calls%20the%20very%20integrity%20of%20the%20blockchain%20into%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20Attorney%20Damian%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%20face%20federal%20charges%20of%20hatching%20a%20plan%20to%20steal%20money%20electronically%20(wire%20fraud)%20and%20then%20disguise%20the%20source%20of%20those%20funds%20(money%20laundering).%20Anton%20Peraire-Bueno%20was%20apprehended%20in%20Boston%2C%20while%20James%20Peraire-Bueno%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Peraire-Bueno%20brothers%20haven't%20commented%20on%20the%20charges%20yet.%20Prosecutors%20claim%20their%20MIT%20education%20in%20computer%20science%20and%20math%20provided%20the%20foundation%20for%20their%20alleged%20crime.%20The%20indictment%20accuses%20them%20of%20spending%20months%20devising%20a%20plan%20to%20exploit%20vulnerabilities%20in%20the%20Ethereum%20blockchain%2C%20the%20system%20that%20verifies%20and%20records%20cryptocurrency%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20allege%20the%20brothers%20found%20a%20loophole%20in%20a%20program%20called%20MEV-boost%2C%20commonly%20used%20by%20Ethereum%20validators%20to%20verify%20transactions.%20By%20exploiting%20this%20weakness%2C%20they%20supposedly%20manipulated%20the%20system%20and%20stole%20the%20cryptocurrency.%20%C2%A0After%20the%20heist%2C%20instead%20of%20returning%20the%20funds%2C%20the%20brothers%20allegedly%20took%20steps%20to%20conceal%20the%20stolen%20money%20through%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20each%20face%20over%2020%20years%20in%20prison%20if%20found%20guilty%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-69018575%5C%22%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715848080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fpds3t6d8_crypto_625x300_09_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmit-graduates-arrested-for-stealing-25-million-in-crypto-in-just-12-seconds-5675685%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anton%20and%20James%20Peraire-Bueno%2C%20aged%2024%20and%2028%20respectively%2C%20allegedly%20manipulated%20the%20Ethereum%20blockchain%20in%20a%20mere%2012%20seconds%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmit-graduates-arrested-for-stealing-25-million-in-crypto-in-just-12-seconds-5675685%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmit-graduates-arrested-for-stealing-25-million-in-crypto-in-just-12-seconds-5675685%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmit-graduates-arrested-for-stealing-25-million-in-crypto-in-just-12-seconds-5675685%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hardik%20Picked%20For%20T20%20WC%20'Under%20Pressure'%3B%20Rohit-Agarkar%20Against%20It%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20rumours%20of%20a%20possible%20rift%20between%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20ever%20since%20the%20latter%20was%20appointed%20captain%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202024.%20Hardik%20had%20replaced%20Rohit%20as%20MI%20captain%20after%20rejoining%20the%20franchise%20from%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(GT)%20during%20the%20trade%20window.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20say%20that%20the%20move%20has%20backfired%20as%20MI%20are%20already%20out%20of%20the%20IPL%202024%20playoffs%20contention.%20Also%2C%20Hardik's%20performance%20this%20season%20has%20been%20mediocre%20to%20say%20the%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2013%20games%2C%20he%20has%20scored%20200%20runs%20at%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20144.93%2C%20while%20also%20taking%2011%20wickets%20in%2013%20matches%20at%20an%20economy%20of%2010.59.%20Most%20of%20his%20good%20bowling%20performances%20have%20come%20in%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Hardik%20was%20still%20picked%20by%20the%20selectors%20in%20the%2015-man%20squad%20for%20the%20upcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20Americas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20had%20recently%20claimed%20that%20neither%20Rohit%20nor%20the%20selection%20committee%2C%20led%20by%20former%20India%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajit%20Agarkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F100-ajit-agarkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAjit%20Agarkar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20selecting%20Hardik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20report%20said%20that%20Hardik%20was%20picked%20in%20the%20team%20under%20'pressure'.%20The%20report%20did%20not%20mention%20whether%20it%20was%20a%20situational%20pressure%20(as%20he%20is%20India's%20top%20fast%20bowling%20allrounder)%20or%20a%20pressure%20from%20some%20quarters.%20The%20report%20also%20attributed%20sources%20as%20saying%20that%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20%2C%20BCCI%20chief%20selector%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20and%20some%20selectors%20were%20against%20Pandya's%20selection%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20team%2C%20during%20the%20selection%20meeting%20in%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fabhishereporter%2Fstatus%2F1789484622436614531%5C%22%3EDainik%20Jagran%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20added%20that%20Rohit%20might%20retire%20from%20the%20T20%20format%20after%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20report%20also%20highlighted%20that%20Hardik's%20place%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%20is%20not%20a%20surity.%20And%20even%20if%20he%20plays%2C%20he%20might%20not%20feature%20in%20all%20of%20the%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Rohit%20and%20Agarkar%20attended%20the%20press%20conference%20after%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad%20selection%2C%20the%20chief%20selector%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Hardik%20in%20the%20roster%20despite%20his%20poor%20form.%20In%20response%2C%20Agarkar%20explained%20how%20the%20selection%20committee%20didn't%20have%20a%20choice%20as%20there's%20no%20like-for-like%20replacement%20for%20Hardik%20available%20from%20the%20talent%20pool%20that%20exists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20play%20three%20of%20their%20four%20Group%20A%20matches%20in%20New%20York%20including%20the%20highly-anticipated%20clash%20with%20Pakistan%20on%20June%209.%20Their%20fourth%20fixture%20is%20slated%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Florida%2C%20against%20Canada%20on%20June%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715848020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ftgmpf03g_rohit-sharma-a