y%20can%20move%20the%20application%20before%20the%20concerned%20court%20and%20thereafter%2C%20the%20court%20can%20only%20grant%20custody%20once%20satisfied%20with%20the%20reasons%20that%20custodial%20interrogation%20is%20required.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BProbe%20Agency%20Can't%20Arrest%20Accused%20If...%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court's%20Big%20Ruling%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20ruling%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20curtailed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fenforcement-directorate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnforcement%20Directorate%3C%2Fa%3E's%20power%20to%20arrest%20an%20accused%20-%20under%20Section%2019%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%20or%20PMLA%20-%20if%20the%20accused%20appears%20as%20summoned%20by%20a%20special%20court%20that%20has%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20cases%20the%20agency%20must%20first%20seek%20that%20court's%20nod%2C%20the%20top%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20cognisance%20is%20taken%20of%20the%20offence...%20the%20ED%20and%20its%20officers%20are%20powerless%20to%20exercise%20powers%20under%20Section%2019%20to%20arrest%20the%20person%20shown%20as%20accused%20in%20the%20complaint%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%2019%20of%20the%20PMLA%20allows%20ED%20officers%20to%20arrest%20an%20individual%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20basis%20of%20material%20in%20possession%20(and)%20reason%20to%20believe%20(to%20be%20recorded%20in%20writing)%20that%20the%20person%20is%20guilty...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%20the%20agency%20must%20inform%20the%20individual%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20may%20be%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20grounds%20for%20the%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20the%20top%20court%20said%20in%20cases%20where%20an%20accused%20was%20not%20arrested%20till%20the%20time%20the%20ED%20filed%20its%20complaint%2C%20they%20could%20not%20be%20arrested%20afterwards.%20The%20special%20court%20must%20first%20issue%20a%20summons%20and%2C%20if%20the%20accused%20duly%20answers%20that%20summons%2C%20they%20could%20not%20been%20seen%20as%20being%20'in%20custody'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20ED%20wants%20custody%20of%20(an)%20accused%20after%20the%20person%20(answers%20a%20special%20court's)%20summons%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20apply%20to%20the%20special%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20Ujjal%20Bhayan%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20custody%20could%20only%20be%20granted%20if%20that%20court%20believes%20custodial%20interrogation%20is%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20arrest%20warrant%20-%20under%20Section%2070%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20-%20can%20only%20be%20issued%20if%20the%20accused%20failed%20to%20answer%20the%20summons%2C%20and%2C%20in%20the%20first%20instance%2C%20this%20must%20be%20a%20bailable%20warrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EALSO%20READ%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-today-enforcement-directorate-cant-keep-filing-chargesheets-to-keep-people-in-jail-observes-top-court-5274968%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCan't%20Keep%20Filing%20Chargesheets%20To%20Keep%20People%20In%20Jail%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20ruling%20-%20one%20seen%20as%20emphasising%20protection%20offered%20from%20arbitrary%20arrest%20by%20the%20central%20agency%20-%20the%20top%20court%20also%20said%20accused%20individuals%20not%20arrested%20before%20answering%20a%20court%20summons%20-%20need%20satisfy%20the%20stringent%20'twin%20test'%20for%20bail%20as%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20PMLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'twin%20test'%20states%20bail%20will%20only%20be%20given%20to%20money%20laundering%20accused%20if%20the%20court%20is%20satisfied%20the%20individual%20is%20not%20guilty%20and%20if%20they%20are%20unlikely%20to%20commit%20crimes%2C%20including%20similar%20offences%2C%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20specific%20background%20to%20this%20ruling%20is%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20in%20which%20the%20accused%20had%20appeared%20before%20a%20special%20court%20as%20summoned.%20The%20question%20then%20was%20if%20the%20accused%20had%20to%20meet%20the%20'twin%20test'%20for%20grant%20of%20bail%20if%20the%20special%20court%20had%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20offence%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20earlier%20reserved%20its%20judgement%20on%20April%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EALSO%20READ%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-hindustan-times-interview-enforcement-directorate-only-3-of-cases-pms-sharp-jab-to-oppositions-probe-agency-claims-5425106%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BOnly%203%25%20Of%20Cases...%26quot%3B%3A%20PM's%20Jab%20To%20Opposition's%20Probe%20Agency%20Claims%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20landmark%20ruling%20comes%20two%20months%20after%20the%20top%20court%20dismissed%20a%20petition%20seeking%20review%20of%20an%20earlier%20verdict%20that%20said%20the%20ED%20is%20required%20to%20furnish%20grounds%20of%20arrest%20to%20an%20accused%20in%20writing%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20exception%26quot%3B%2C%20saying%20there%20was%20no%20error%20in%20its%20judgement%20warranting%20reconsideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20court%20had%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3Bmere%20non-cooperation%20of%20a%20witness%2C%20in%20response%20to%20summons%20issued%20under%20Section%2050%2C%20will%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20render%20him%2Fher%20liable%20to%20arrest%20under%20Section%2019%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715847780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fc1l320oo_supreme-court-ani_625x300_23_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-enforcement-directorate-section-19-pmla-probe-agency-cant-arrest-accused-if-supreme-courts-big-ruling-5675220%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20cannot%20arrest%20an%20accused%20-%20under%20Section%2019%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%20or%20PMLA%20-%20if%20they%20appear%20as%20summoned%20by%20a%20special%20court%20that%20has%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20complaint.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-enforcement-directorate-section-19-pmla-probe-agency-cant-arrest-accused-if-supreme-courts-big-ruling-5675220%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-enforcement-directorate-section-19-pmla-probe-agency-cant-arrest-accused-if-supreme-courts-big-ruling-5675220%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-enforcement-directorate-section-19-pmla-probe-agency-cant-arrest-accused-if-supreme-courts-big-ruling-5675220%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aide%20Summoned%20By%20Women's%20Panel%20Over%20Swati%20Maliwal%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fbibhav-kumar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBibhav%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20Delhi%