ch%20said%20it%20was%20made%20in%20Israel%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaken%20aback%2C%20he%20started%20researching%20more%20on%20how%20a%20dry%20and%20hot%20country%20like%20Israel%20can%20grow%20avocados.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsh%20started%20with%20a%20few%20plants%20and%20now%20has%20a%2010%20acre%20farm.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350002%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsh%20started%20with%20a%20few%20plants%20and%20now%20has%20a%2010-acre%20farm.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20soil%20and%20temperature%20it%20needed%20to%20grow.%20It%20needs%20a%20temperature%20below%2030%20degrees%20and%20acidic%20soil%20with%20good%20drainage.%20I%20was%20very%20intrigued%20and%20wanted%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20how%20Israel%20did%20it%20with%20such%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F139546%2Ftemperatures-water-atms-bengaluru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20temperatures%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%