0of%20this%20amount%20to%20buy%20one%20%3Cem%3Etola%20%3C%2Fem%3E(nearly%2012%20grams)%20of%20gold%20to%20secure%20the%20future%20of%20my%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1-1715763906.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Collectively%2C%20these%20women%20diverted%2020%2C000%20kg%20of%20waste%20to%20something%20useful.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1-1715763906.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1-1715763906-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1-1715763906-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1-1715763906-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1-1715763906-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350010%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECollectively%2C%20these%20women%20diverted%2020%2C000%20kg%20of%20waste%20to%20something%20useful.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20these%20rural%20women%20have%20sold%20about%2012%2C000%20products%20and%20have%20established%20a%20large%20customer%20base%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20social%20angle%20is%20one%20of%20the%20contributing%20factors%2C%20our%20products%20have%20also%20become%20popular%20for%20their%20durability%20and%20better%20finish%20compared%20to%20other%20eco-friendly%20products%20like%20bamboo.%20While%20bamboo%20products%20are%20prone%20to%20fungal%20attack%2C%20there%20