een%20instrumental%20in%20developing%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20moss%20garden%20in%20Nainital%20which%20boasts%20around%2090%20different%20types%20of%20moss%20species%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F248029%2Fwoman-entrepreneur-pathanamthitta-kerala-moss-rose-cinderella-jumbo-table-rose-covid-19-pandemic-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen-air%20fernery%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Ranikhet%20with%20200%20different%20types%20of%20ferns%20and%20a%20grass%20conservatory%20in%20Ranikhet%20with%20more%20than%20100%20grass%20species.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20always%20underestimate%20the%20importance%20of%20grasses%2C%20but%20the%20latest%20research%20shows%20them%20to%20be%20more%20effective%20in%20carbon%20sequestration%20than%20trees%20because%20they%20store%20carbon%20in%20their%20roots%20instead%20of%20releasing%20it%20into%20the%20atmosphere.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Chaturvedi%20shies%20away%20from%20accepting%20applause.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20says%2C%20if%20there%20is%20anyone%20that%20deserves%20the%20praise%20it%20is%20Mother%20Nature.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20huge%20respect%20for%20her.%20She%20has%20designed%20each%20and%20everything%20in%20such%20a%20connected%20manner%3B%20every%20moss%2C%20every%20lichen%2C%20every%20insect%2C%20every%20pollinator.%20They%20are%20all%20so%20beautifully%20interconnected%20with%20each%20other%20that%20if%20you%20take%20out%20even%20one%20string%2C%20the%20entire%20chain%20will%20be%20disturbed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715610366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349417%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IFS%20officer%20Sanjeev%20Chaturvedi%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20save%20and%20fos