0to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347926%2Fcerelac-sugar-nestle-babies-infants-health-nutrition-report-meal-plan-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraise%20a%20child%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ask%20any%20mother%2C%20and%20she%20will%20agree.%20Earlier%2C%20these%20villages%20were%20found%20quite%20literally%2C%20in%20homes%2C%20and%20neighbourhoods.%20When%20we%20were%20growing%20up%2C%20we%20would%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20playing%20downstairs%20or%20in%20our%20neighbours%E2%80%99%20houses.%20In%20joint%20family%20settings%2C%20the%20village%20was%20present%20within%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20increasingly%20nuclear%20households%2C%20we%2C%20as%20mothers%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20that%20privilege.%20This%20leads%20us%20to%20look%20for%20villages%20in%20the%20virtual%20world.%20Since%20we%20also%20want%20to%20raise%20our%20children%20using%20modern%20methods%20and%2C%20often%20being%20single%20children%20or%20having%20just%20one%20sibling%2C%20we%20tend%20to%20seek%20support%20from%20peers%20experiencing%20similar%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20navigating%20the%20challenging%20postpartum%20period%20to%20receiving%20tips%20on%20feeding%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20breastfeeding%20or%20formula%20%E2%80%94%20and%20starting%20solids%2C%20sleep%20training%2C%20and%20much%20more%2C%20virtual%20support%20groups%20have%20become%20a%20new%20mother%E2%80%99s%20go-to%20village%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%20The%20questions%20mentioned%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20common%20ones%20you%20can%20find%20in%20any%20new%20mother%E2%80%99s%20support%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCzK2B4zpnAB%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCzK2B4zpnAB%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCzK2B4zpnAB%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20New%20Mother%20(%40newmother.in)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20I%20found%20abundant%20help%20through%20these%20groups%20on%20Facebook%20and%20WhatsApp%2C%20where%20one%20can%20ask%20questions%20without%20fear%20of%20judgment%20and%20receive%20instant%20replies%20from%20the%20thousands%20of%20moms%20who%20are%20either%20going%20through%20the%20same%20dilemma%20or%20have%20already%20passed%20that%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2032-year-old%20Rohini%E2%80%99s%20example.%20The%20first-time%20mother%20had%20a%20complicated%20pregnancy%20that%20led%20to%20her%20facing%20severe%20postpartum%20depression.%20Her%20friend%20coerced%20her%20to%20join%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20for%20new%20mothers%2C%20where%20she%20found%20instant%20answers%20to%20her%20many%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20unable%20to%20breastfeed%20and%20was%20pressured%20to%20give%20formula%20by%20the%20elders%20at%20home.%20This%20gradually%20led%20to%20a%20reduction%20in%20my%20breast%20milk%2C%20adding%20to%20my%20guilt.%20I%20found%20many%20contacts%20for%20lactation%20consultants%20through%20this%20group%2C%20through%20which%20I%20worked%20on%20increasing%20breast%20milk%20supply%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohini%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20though%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20is%20the%20sisterhood%20she%20found%20through%20this%20group.%20While%20a%20set%20of%20mothers%20advised%20her%20on%20how%20she%20could%20improve%20her%20milk%20supply%2C%20another%20set%20also%20assuaged%20her%20by%20saying%20there%20was%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20giving%20formula%20to%20a%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20made%20me%20understand%20that%20a%20fed%20baby%20is%20what%20matters%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20which%20took%20a%20huge%20load%20off%20my%20back.%20I%20could%20vent%20and%20share%20the%20tiniest%20of%20troubles%2C%20and%20there%20was%20always%20somebody%20to%20listen.%20This%20group%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20blessings%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20ABCs%20of%20feeding%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20the%20WhatsApp%20group%20Rohini%20is%20a%20part%20of%2C%20there%20are%20several%20others%20on%20the%20platform.%20While%20many%20such%20groups%20have%20shifted%20to%20WhatsApp%20due%20to%20ease%20of%20access%2C%20this%20movement%20of%20sorts%20really%20began%20on%20Facebook%2C%20sometime%20in%20the%202010s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20question%20that%20any%20new%20mother%20has%20after%20the%20birth%20of%20her%20child%20is%20about%20breastfeeding%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20requirement%20of%20such%20a%20group%20essential.%20Adhunika%20Prakash%20found%20herself%20alone%20in%20Ireland%20as%20she%20navigated%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F255089%2Fdr-m-aishwarya-coimbatore-parenting-network-tamil-nadu-taboo-how-to-donate-breast-milk-feeding-awareness-taboo-myths-banks-postpartum-depression-covid-19-pandemic-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equestions%20around%20breastfeeding%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20motherhood.%20She%20found%20support%20on%20an%20Irish%20breastfeeding%20group%20on%20Facebook.%20Not%20finding%20a%20similar%20one%20in%20India%2C%20she%20started%20%E2%80%98Breastfeeding%20Support%20For%20Indian%20Mothers%E2%80%99%20(BSIM)%20in%202013%2C%20which%20has%20grown%20into%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20communities%20online%2C%20with%20almost%201.5%20lakh%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20lonely%20and%20had%20no%20one%20to%20talk%20to%20about%20the%20challenges%20I%20was%20facing.%20I%20found%20that%20many%20of%20my%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20too%20had%20similar%20queries.%20Fact%20is%2C%20no%20one%20talks%20about%20how%20difficult%20the%20journey%20of%20breastfeeding%20and%20motherhood%20is.%20I%20started%20this%20group%20for%20mothers%20to%20unite%20and%20get%20answers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adhunika%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20community%2C%20through%20experts%20such%20as%20lactation%20counsellors%20and%20educators%2C%20offers%20tips%20and%20accurate%20information%20on%20lactation%2C%20how%20to%20wean%20off%20formula%2C%20and%20more.%20Besides%20the%20experts%2C%20other%20mothers%20too%20weigh%20in%20and%20share%20tips%20through%20their%20own%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBSIM%20was%20named%20one%20of%20the%20top%20five%20Facebook%20groups%20in%20the%20world%20in%202018%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20reach.%20Besides%20creating%20a%20community%2C%20BSIM%20also%20conducts%20webinars%20and%20offers%20one-on-one%20lactation%20consultation%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20common%20questions%20that%20the%20group%20receives%20are%20around%20breastfeeding%20post%20six%20months%2C%20and%20weaning%20off%20formula%2C%20informs%20Adhunika%2C%20who%20has%20also%20written%20a%20book%20called%20Breast%20Potion%2C%20advocating%20breastfeeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-bl