-fed%20her%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20mothers%20begin%20finding%20a%20rhythm%20with%20feeding%2C%20the%20next%20big%20challenge%20is%20starting%20solids.%20There%20are%20two%20popular%20methods%20followed%20among%20new%20mothers%20%E2%80%94%20one%20being%20traditional%20weaning%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20the%20parents%20feeding%20the%20child%2C%20also%20called%20spoon-feeding%2C%20and%20the%20other%20being%20baby-led%20weaning%20(BLW)%2C%20where%20the%20baby%20is%20encouraged%20to%20eat%20by%20himself%20or%20herself%20right%20from%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20transition%20is%20a%20very%20confusing%20time%20for%20new%20mothers%20%E2%80%94%20right%20from%20deciding%20which%20method%20to%20follow%2C%20what%20to%20offer%2C%20how%20much%20to%20offer%2C%20when%20to%20offer%2C%20and%20much%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Facebook%20groups%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Traditional%20Weaning%20(Introducing%20Solids)%20India%2C%20with%20over%201.4%20lakh%20members%2C%20and%20Baby%20Led%20Weaning%20for%20Indian%20babies%20%E2%80%93%20Recipes%20and%20Techniques%2C%20with%20over%2045%2C000%20members%20%E2%80%94%20and%20many%20WhatsApp%20groups%20again%20come%20to%20the%20rescue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20these%20groups%2C%20many%20nutritionists%20and%20new%20mothers%20are%20offering%20useful%20tips%20and%20tricks%20on%20Instagram%20through%20live%20sessions%20and%20even%20providing%20quick%20replies%20to%20their%20direct%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtUWYXcrUO6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtUWYXcrUO6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C