0activities%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20destination%2C%20Palighar%20is%20outside%20the%20town%20area%20of%20Kalimpong.%20The%20guests%20who%20ideally%20come%20and%20stay%20with%20us%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20calm%20vacation%20and%20that%20is%20what%20we%20try%20to%20give%20them.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20guests%20arrive%2C%20the%20couple%20briefs%20them%20about%20the%20property%20and%20the%20surroundings.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20they%20have%20settled%20in%2C%20we%20also%20give%20them%20a%20list%20of%20activities%20that%20we%20do.%20The%20guests%20can%20walk%20with%20us%20and%20trek%20to%20the%20villages%20nearby%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kabir%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20trek%2C%20we%20encourage%20them%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20villagers%20and%20understand%20their%20ways%20of%20living.%20If%20our%20guests%20are%20interested%2C%20we%20also%20explain%20the%20various%20aspects%20of%20terrace%20farming%20with%20a%20live%20demonstration.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20common%20practice%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20guests%20can%20also%20go%20on%20a%20longer%20trek%20to%20River%20Relli%2C%20where%20they%20can%20have%20a%20small%20picnic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20hold%20cooking%20classes%20for%20the%20guests%20who%20want%20to%20cook%20our%20traditional%20dishes.%20The%20dishes%20that%20are%20served%20are%20all%20traditional%20Nepali%2C%20Tibetan%20and%20Bhutanese%20dishes%20used%20with%20ingredients%20from%20our%20farm%20and%20the%20surrounding%20farms%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-6-1-1715264286.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20is%20built%20using%20bamboo%20and%20mud.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5