dered.%20Alongside%20languages%20and%20math%2C%20students%20explore%20diverse%20subjects%20through%20practical%20experiences%20and%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20recently%2C%20the%20students%20completed%20a%20board%20game%20project%20where%20they%20designed%20and%20created%20their%20own%20board%20games%2C%20complete%20with%20unique%20rules.%20Students%20are%20encouraged%20to%20delve%20deeply%20into%20subjects%20of%20their%20choosing%20and%20conduct%20in-depth%20studies%20according%20to%20their%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20organisation%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20children's%20education%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20shelter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349409%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20organisation%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20education%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20shelter.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmeen%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20living%20in%20Pathshala%20hostel%20and%20has%20been%20with%20Juin%20for%20over%20four%20years%2C%20shares%20his%20perspective%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20enriching%20aspect%20of%20our%20education%20is%20a%20class%20where%20we%20learn%20without%20textbooks.%20We%20select%20a%20topic%2C%20discuss%20it%2C%20and%20learn%20from%20each%20other%20and%20our%20teachers.%20Moreover%2C%20our%20educators%20stress%20on%20understanding%20concepts%20deeply%20rather%20than%20just%20memorisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20second%20chance%20at%20life%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20these%20kids%20have%20a%20safe%20place%20here%20to%20thrive%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20their%20lives%20still%20lingers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jui.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20hail%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20travel%20frequently%2C%20leaving%20their%20children%20under%20my%20care.%20Yet%2C%20upon%20returning%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20these%20children%20confront%20challenges%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20face%20at%20such%20tender%20ages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recalls%20a%20distressing%20incident%20during%20their%20summer%20vacation%20when%20she%20encountered%20one%20of%20her%20students%20begging%20on%20the%20streets.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20children%20who%20stay%20with%20us%20leave%20for%20summer%20vacations%20to%20their%20homes.%20While%20we%20try%20to%20give%20them%20the%20best%20life%20here%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20poverty%20they%20were%20born%20into%20hits%20hard.%20It%20was%20during%20one%20of%20these%20vacation%20days%20that%20I%20saw%20one%20of%20my%20students%20begging.%20It%20was%20heart-wrenching%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20upset.%20I%20spoke%20to%20their%20parents%2C%20but%20the%20mother%20simply%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98How%20will%20they%20eat%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20beg%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FSupport-Srotoshwini-Trust%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22