india.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-10-at-10.50.45-min-1715318691-150x106.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349603%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221129%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20founders%20conduct%20awareness%20programs%20in%20schools%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20struck%20the%20nation%2C%20interrupting%20their%20grand%20launch%2C%20the%20four%20friends%20returned%20to%20their%20drawing%20board%20to%20chalk%20out%20new%20plans%20to%20avert%20the%20setback.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20Shashidhar%20suggested%20venturing%20into%20the%20vegan%20ice%20cream%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98What%20would%20an%20Indian%20alternative%20to%20almond%20or%20oats%20milk%20be%3F%E2%80%99%20they%20wondered.%20Prabu%20recalled%20his%20visit%20to%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20he%20had%20seen%20milk%20being%20extracted%20from%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20given%20to%20children.%20With%20this%20insight%2C%20they%20thought%20%E2%80%98Why%20not%20extract%20milk%20from%20millets%20and%20convert%20it%20into%20ice%20cream%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20thought%20led%20them%20to%20launch%20their%20hero%20product%20%E2%80%94%20millet%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20worked%20out%20of%20a%20300%20sqft%20space%20in%20Trichy%2C%20where%20they%20procured%20machines%20and%20started%20working%20on%20ways%20to%20extract%20milk%20from%20different%20millets.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20six%20months%2C%20they%20found%20that%20the%20major%20millets%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%2C%20bajra%2C%20ragi%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20foxtail%20millet%20%E2%80%94%20produced%20good%20results.%20They%20then%20experimented%20with%20different%20sweeteners%20and%20fruits%2C%20and%20developed%20these%20ice-creams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20made-in-India%20vegan%20ice-cream%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20six%20months%20of%20research%20and%